223
00:20:33,590 --> 00:20:33,983
Ji Xiang.

224
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:36,720
Bagaimana sifat Kapten Kelompok
Bajak Laut Mutiara Ungu?

225
00:20:36,720 --> 00:20:37,750
Dia sangat baik.

226
00:20:37,750 --> 00:20:39,420
Sering memberi uang pada
nelayan miskin.

227
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:41,190
Siapa yang mengikat kalian di sini?

228
